{
  "title": "Observing Cron-Driven Tasks Using FastAPI with Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This guide explains how to set up and monitor cron jobs within a FastAPI application in Python 3.12+. It covers creating a Health API, setting up a Cron job, and handling requests for status updates.",
  "key_points": [
    "Use FastAPI for building the API",
    "Create a Health API endpoint",
    "Set up a Cron job to trigger the FastAPI app",
